---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Welcome">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="!mt-0 !mb-2">Welcome to the UIUC CS Wiki</h1>
      <p class="text-wiki-muted text-lg">A student-maintained guide to Computer Science at Illinois</p>
    </div>

    <div class="not-prose mb-8 rounded-xl border border-wiki-border bg-wiki-surface p-6">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-illinois-orange/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-illinois-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-wiki-text">About This Wiki</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-wiki-muted">
            This wiki is independently maintained by students, for students, as a guide to CS and CS-adjacent courses at UIUC. 
            We're always looking for contributors to help keep information up-to-date!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Using the Wiki</h2>
    
    <div class="not-prose grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 mb-8">
      <a href="/classes" class="group rounded-xl border border-wiki-border bg-wiki-surface p-5 transition-colors hover:border-illinois-orange/50 hover:bg-wiki-surface/80">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-illinois-orange/20">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-illinois-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-wiki-text group-hover:text-illinois-orange transition-colors">Classes</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-wiki-muted">
          Detailed information on CS, MATH, and STAT courses including difficulty, workload, and student tips.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/resources" class="group rounded-xl border border-wiki-border bg-wiki-surface p-5 transition-colors hover:border-illinois-blue/50 hover:bg-wiki-surface/80">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-illinois-blue/20">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-illinois-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-wiki-text group-hover:text-illinois-blue transition-colors">Resources</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-wiki-muted">
          Tutoring services, career resources, software tools, and student organizations.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides" class="group rounded-xl border border-wiki-border bg-wiki-surface p-5 transition-colors hover:border-green-500/50 hover:bg-wiki-surface/80">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-500/20">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-wiki-text group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">Guides</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-wiki-muted">
          Step-by-step guides for internships, research, grad school, and more.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/curriculum" class="group rounded-xl border border-wiki-border bg-wiki-surface p-5 transition-colors hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:bg-wiki-surface/80">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-purple-500/20">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-wiki-text group-hover:text-purple-500 transition-colors">Curriculum</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-wiki-muted">
          Interactive curriculum graphs and example schedules for different tracks.
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Who Made This?</h2>
    <p>
      This wiki is maintained by UIUC CS students who want to help other students navigate the curriculum. 
      We accept contributions from any Illinois students and review new content for quality and accuracy before publishing.
    </p>

    <h2>Contributing</h2>
    <p>
      We manage contributions on <a href="https://github.com">GitHub</a>. Please feel free to open a pull request 
      by following the readme there. You can contribute course reviews, add new guides, or fix any errors you find.
    </p>

    <div class="not-prose mt-8 rounded-xl border border-yellow-500/30 bg-yellow-500/10 p-5">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-yellow-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-yellow-500">Disclaimer</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-wiki-muted">
            This wiki contains opinions and experiences from students. Always verify important information 
            with official university resources and your academic advisor.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
